# DESIGN GUIDELINES

## Purpose

Define visual direction, token usage, and component styling rules for Desire Escorts to ensure consistent implementation across templates and prevent design drift during migration.

## Visual Direction

Premium dark aesthetic with warm gold luminosity. The design uses subtle gradient washes to create depth and atmosphere against dark surfaces, with 3D-beveled interactive elements that feel tactile and luxurious.

**Core principles:**
- Dark-first surface hierarchy (Carbon Black base, Dark Olive cards)
- Gold accents used sparingly for emphasis and interaction
- Subtle ambient gradients to add warmth without distraction
- High contrast maintained for accessibility on all text
- Tactile, beveled CTAs that feel premium and clickable

